Package com.olegtoropoff.petcareappointment.dto

Class UserDto

java.lang.Object
com.olegtoropoff.petcareappointment.dto.UserDto
public class UserDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) for representing user details. This class is used to transfer user-related data between different layers of the application, ensuring separation between the persistence and presentation layers.
